Introduction

Ayden is a South Korean rapper under C9 Entertainment. In 2021, he made his official debut as the lead rapper of the boy group EPEX. He was revealed as the 8th and final member to join the group. He officially debuted in 2021with the mini-album ‘BIPOLAR Pt. 1: Prelude of Anxiety’.
